reviews.review_text: Just leave it to Charlie Of the Audience recordings of this show, this one sounds the best on my computer.  Another good sounding Aud is the Amick/Prescott version of this show.
Playin' For me, the most peaceful moment of any Dead tune is when they break into the first jam in Playin'. It's like they gently push away from a dock and float away. Beautiful.
